 24. 🌐 What is an API Gateway?
 ==========================================================================
 -> An API Gateway is a single entry point for all client requests in a microservices architecture.
 -> Instead of the client calling each microservice directly, all requests go through the API Gateway, which then routes them 
    to the appropriate service.
    
    ❌ Without API Gateway (Problem)
    
    Client → User Service
    Client → Order Service
    Client → Payment Service
