      1️- Circuit Breaker 🔌
               Stops calling a failed service
      2- Retry 🔁
               Retry failed requests a few times
      3️- Fallback 🛟
               Provide alternate response         
      4️- Timeout ⏱
               Don’t wait forever for response
      5- Load Balancing ⚖
               Distribute load across instances
               
